<HR align="center" width="75%"><P>

 Hello, Milo. I would like to thank you for writing a great column. Reading some of your replies to previous questions, it seems you like to talk
about sex. Now here is my question: How many times do you get laid per week?<P>

 James Nesta

<P> <P><b><i>
